ctory Medical Report (Form B enclosed).</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><strong>RESIDENCE PERMIT</strong><br />\r\nAll foreign students are required to apply for a Residence Permit from their nearest Tanzanian Embassy before they depart for Tanzania.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><strong>IDENTITY CARD</strong><br />\r\nA Student Identity Card will be issued to you after you have completed University registration formalities and only then will you be allowed to use University facilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\">Finally, I wish to take this opportunity to congratulate you for this offer and to wish you a happy stay and success in your studies at this University.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\">Yours faithfully,</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost/admission/web/img/institution/signature.jpg\" style=\"height:46px; width:80px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\">Dr. Egbert Mujuni</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><strong>Director of Undergraduate Studies</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><strong>Encls</strong>: Registration Form &ldquo;A&rdquo;, Medical Examination Form &ldquo;B&rdquo;, (these have to be filled and submitted during registration), Fresher&rsquo;s Joining Instructions and UDSM Revised Fee Structure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n',0,0,NULL,NULL,'2020-04-11 18:43:15',7);
